    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for someone needing a dependable daily driver on a budget. The engine and transmission are both fully functional and have been regularly serviced, though the car does show its age with some noticeable cosmetic wear, including minor scratches on the exterior and some fading on the interior upholstery. There are no major mechanical issues, but you can expect some typical signs of use consistent with its history. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done without any hidden surprises.",
