    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition. The exterior shows minor signs of use but is free of major dents or deep scratches. The interior is well-maintained with only light wear on the seats. Mechanically, the car is reliable and has been regularly serviced.",
