    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who prioritizes function over aesthetics. The engine and transmission are in good working order, though the exterior shows significant signs of age, including several noticeable scratches, a few small dents on the door panels, and some fading of the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat, but all electronics and climate controls remain fully operational. It has been regularly serviced, and while it isn't a showpiece, it remains a dependable choice for practical transportation.",
      "price": 22500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of fastidious care. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, confirms its status as a premier example of the marque. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle offers an unparalleled ownership opportunity.",
      "price": 46500.0,
